did.unittitle: Yale College records concerning teaching fellows

did.abstract: The records consist of appointments, correspondence, and financial records documenting departmental teaching fellows at Yale College.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-E (YRG 9-E), Records documenting Yale College offices, programs, and projects.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale College Records Concerning Teaching Fellows (RU 574). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of appointments, correspondence, and financial records documenting departmental teaching fellows at Yale College.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.
